Australia Pty Ltd v Victoria </i>  <a href="http://www.austlii.edu.au/au/cases/cth/HCA/2002/27.html" title="View Case" class="autolink_findcases">[2002] HCA 27</a>, para 183: 'the problems to which
I have just referred are likely to be aggravated by the increasingly competitive
