of Australia Act </i>1976</a> (Cth)' <a href="http://www.austlii.edu.au/au/journals/MelbULawRw/1994/5.html" title="View Case" class="autolink_findcases_inserted">[1994] MelbULawRw 5</a>;  <a href="/cgi-bin/LawCite?cit=%281994%29%2019%20Melbourne%20University%20Law%20Review%20615" title="View LawCiteRecord" class="autolink_findcases">(1994) 19 <i>Melbourne University Law Review
