<p><sup><a name="fn23" href="#fnB23">[22]</a></sup> 	<i>Philip Morris </i><a href="http://www.austlii.edu.au/au/cases/cth/FCA/2000/229.html" title="View Case" class="autolink_findcases_inserted">[2000] FCA 229</a>;  <a href="/cgi-bin/LawCite?cit=%282000%29%20170%20ALR%20487" title="View LawCiteRecord" class="autolink_findcases">(2000)
