represent smokers with disease but rather was brought on behalf of health and
medical
organisations and smokers not yet diagnosed with smoking-related disease
in order to establish a fund under <a href="http://www.austlii.edu.au/au/legis/cth/num_act/tpa1974149/s87.html" class="autolink_findacts">Section 87</a> of the <i><a href="http://www.austlii.edu.au/au/legis/cth/num_act/tpa1974149/" class="autolink_findacts">Trade Practices Act 1974</a>
</i>(Cth).</p>
