<p><sup><a name="fn54" href="#fnB54">[53]</a></sup> 	See <i>Bright v Femcare Ltd
</i>  <a href="http://www.austlii.edu.au/au/cases/cth/FCA/2000/742.html" title="View Case" class="autolink_findcases">[2000] FCA 742</a>, para 81 (Lehane J); <i>Batten v CTMS Ltd </i>  <a href="http://www.austlii.edu.au/au/cases/cth/FCA/2000/915.html" title="View Case" class="autolink_findcases">[2000] FCA 915</a>;
